Name: Black clay coffee mug
Short description: Sleek water pitcher with advanced filtration system and built-in filter replacement indicator.
Description: The AquaPure Filtered Water Pitcher features a state-of-the-art filtration system that removes impurities and chlorine from tap water, ensuring a clean and refreshing taste. With its sleek, ergonomic design and a capacity of 10 cups, it’s perfect for everyday use. The pitcher also includes a built-in indicator to let you know when it’s time to replace the filter.

Name: Blue ceramic plant pot with saucer
Short description: Airtight, leak-proof food storage containers that keep food fresh and are microwave and dishwasher safe.
Description: EverFresh Food Storage Containers come in a set of five with airtight, leak-proof lids that keep your food fresh longer. Made from BPA-free, durable plastic, these containers are microwave, dishwasher, and freezer safe. Their stackable design ensures easy storage and organization in your pantry or fridge.

Name: Jade flower vase, blue
Short description: Soft memory foam bath mat with a non-slip backing, offering comfort and quick drying.
Description: The LuxeComfort Memory Foam Bath Mat provides plush cushioning and superior absorbency right out of the shower. Made with a high-density memory foam core and a non-slip backing, it offers both comfort and safety. The soft, machine-washable cover dries quickly and adds a touch of luxury to your bathroom.

Name: Blue ceramic serving dish
Short description: Stainless steel coffee filter that’s reusable and eco-friendly, offering rich flavor and easy cleaning.
Description: The EcoBrew Reusable Coffee Filter is designed to provide a sustainable and eco-friendly alternative to disposable paper filters. Made from stainless steel mesh, it fits most standard coffee makers and ensures a full-bodied, rich coffee flavor. Its easy-to-clean design makes it a convenient and environmentally-conscious choice.

Name: Gray ceramic flower vase
Short description: Compact induction cooktop with precise temperature control and rapid heating for efficient cooking.
Description: The ZenCook Induction Cooktop is a compact and efficient portable cooking solution with precise temperature control and rapid heating capabilities. Featuring a sleek touch-control panel and multiple cooking modes, it’s perfect for quick meals or as an extra burner in your kitchen. Its easy-to-clean surface and safety features make it a practical addition to any kitchen.

Name: Rustic decorative plant pot
Short description: Ultrasonic diffuser with adjustable mist settings and LED light for a calming aromatic experience.
Description: The SereneBreeze Ultrasonic Essential Oil Diffuser uses ultrasonic technology to disperse your favorite essential oils into a fine mist, creating a calming and aromatic atmosphere. With adjustable mist settings and a built-in LED light that can cycle through various colors, it’s perfect for enhancing relaxation in any room. The diffuser also features an automatic shut-off function for safety.

Name: Blue ceramic serving round dish
Short description: Automated robot vacuum with advanced navigation and powerful suction for effortless cleaning.

With programmable cleaning schedules and a large dustbin, it’s designed to keep your floors spotless with minimal effort.
